OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 23 Jun to Thu 2 Jul
OL,6,FProbably a north-south split at the
OL,7,Fstart of this period. Many areas in
OL,8,Fthe south will be mainly fine and dry
OL,9,Fwith temperatures well above normal,
OL,10,Falbeit with a small risk of a few
OL,11,Fshowers or thunderstorms at times. In
OL,12,Fthe north, changeable with some
OL,13,Fshowers or spells of rain, perhaps
OL,14,Fheavy at times, and temperatures near
OL,15,Fnormal, although with drier, brighter
OL,16,Fperiods also. Into late June, high
OL,17,Fpressure may begin to build with
OL,18,Fconditions becoming more widely dry
OL,19,Fand settled. Temperatures are likely
OL,20,Fto be above normal for many areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
